OL,3,CTrapped researchers in Antarctica call
OL,4,Cfor help after 'assault' of colleague
OL,6,FA group of scientists at a remote base
OL,7,Fin Antarctica have asked for
OL,8,F"immediate action" after a member of
OL,9,Fthe team reportedly physically
OL,10,Fassaulted and threatened to kill
OL,11,Fanother colleague.
OL,13,FThe researchers are in total isolation
OL,14,Fat South Africa's Sanae IV base, and
OL,15,Fare reported to have ten months left
OL,16,Fof their 16 month expedition.
