OL,3,CTrapped researchers in Antarctica call
OL,4,Cfor help after 'assault' of colleague
OL,6,FLocated in the Queen Maud Land region,
OL,7,Fthe base is 80 kilometres inland on a
OL,8,Fnunatak - a mountain ridge that
OL,9,Fprotrudes from a glacier - and is
OL,10,Fcompletely surrounded by glacial sheet.
OL,12,FIts remote location combined with
OL,13,Fextreme weather conditions can make it
OL,14,Fdifficult to reach.
OL,16,FA message from one of the researchers
OL,17,Fshared with South Africa's Sunday
OL,18,FTimes said they were "deeply
OL,19,Fconcerned" about their own safety due
OL,20,Fto a colleagues behaviour.
