OL,3,CTrapped researchers in Antarctica call
OL,4,Cfor help after 'assault' of colleague
OL,6,FThe researcher said the team member
OL,7,Fhad also been accused of sexual
OL,8,Fassault, adding that his behaviour had
OL,9,Fbecome "increasingly egregious".
OL,11,F"It is imperative that immediate
OL,12,Faction is taken to ensure my safety
OL,13,Fand the safety of all employees," the
OL,14,Fmessage continued.
OL,16,FSouth Africa's environment minister,
OL,17,FDion George, is reported to have
OL,18,Fconfirmed the incident, adding he
OL,19,Fwould personally speak to the team
OL,20,Fmembers.
