OL,4,Cfor help after 'assault' of colleague
OL,6,FThe base has three modules and
OL,7,Fincludes a helicopter hanger, sauna
OL,8,Fand hospital.
OL,10,FAround ten team members remain at the
OL,11,Fbase in total isolation until the next
OL,12,Fteam arrives between December to
OL,13,FMarch, according to the Antarctic
OL,14,FLegacy of South Africa (ALSA) website.
